Manchester United beat Manchester City 4-1 in the Manchester derby at Old Trafford on Sunday . 
  United manager Louis van Gaal left Angel di Maria and Radamel Falcao on the bench . 
  Ashley Young, Marouane Fellaini and Juan Mata scored in the win . 
  Manchester City have lost five of their last six Premier League games . 
  Manuel Pellegrini has overseen a period of decline at City . 
 